mods.abstract: The plan is part of a letter sent from the Political Agent, Muscat to the Muscat and Oman, Council of Ministers. The plan highlights the areas of ground suitable for landing, the rough stony ground, and other elements of the work to be done at Bait Al-Falaj landing ground.
